tool_description: The most complete and cheap Fake Identity Generation API
title: Fake Identity Generator

api_list.name: GenerateIdentity
api_list.description: Use this endpoint is for generate a fake identity specifying gender and age, click the test button and enjoy the informations generated!

optional_parameters.name: age
optional_parameters.description:
int number between 16 and 70 (including extremes and integer numbers only)
If omitted it will be randomly extracted

optional_parameters.name: gender
optional_parameters.description:
Possible values: "m", "f" (case unsesnsitive)
If omitted it will be randomly extracted

api_list.name: GenerateRandomIdentity
api_list.description: Use this endpoint to generate a random fake identity, click the test button and enjoy the informations generated!
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://fake-identity-generator1.p.rapidapi.com/GenerateRandomIdentity.php"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "fake-identity-generator1.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
